1 Un cheeloghooilley ren mee er chur mow,
2 myr share ghow mee daa hooilley,
3 as eisht ren eh cur my chymlaghym mow;

10 Ayns shoh va ny s’lea nagh ny s’jerree,
11 myr shen va my eddin goll er my raad;
12 agh cheayll mee fed corneil ard,

19 Va mee goll er ny h-eiyrtyssyn beggan,
20 as ren eh cosoylagh rish my laue dy vel beggan ard-hurdyssyn;
21 as dooyrt mee: «Ynseyder, insh, cre'n thalloo t'ayn shoh?».

25 Hig oo dy mie, my ta oo çheet stiagh ayns shen,
26 kys ta’n chioneys goll er-skyn veih foddey;
27 shen-y-fa, cur ort hene dy vie ny skeealey.

58 Vaghin dy eddin, myr vaghtal, liauyr as mooar,
59 myr pinneydysh Noo Shenn Peddyr ayns Rome,
60 as myr shen va ny çhibbyn elley echey;

64 jannoo ymmyrkey mooar dy roshtyn huggey;
65 son va mee fakin tree feed phalm mooar
66 veih’n ynnyd sheese raad ta dooinney kiangley yn edd echey.

73 Jean ronsaghey er dty chleeau, as gheddys y stroin
74 t’eh kiangley rish, oh annymh cha nel ayd;
75 as jeeagh er y fer shen t’eh dogging dty chleeau mooar».

76 Eisht dooyrt eh rhym, «T’eh hene t’eh cur yn ourys er e hene;
77 she Nembrod t’ayn, as er coontey yn drogh-obbraghey echey
78 cha nel agh un çhengey erbee ayns y theihll.»

79 Faag er, as ny loayr shin dy jarroo;
80 son myr shen t’eh dagh çhengey da,
81 myr t’eh echey hene da deiney elley, as cha nel eh ayn fockle erbee ayn.

94 Fïalte yn ennym eie, as ren eh ny obbraghyn mooarey
95 traa dy row ny gigantyn jannoo aggle er y vooar-hee'ryn;
96 cha nel eh nish goll dy chruinnaghey ny laueyn ren eh chleayney».

124 Ny cur shin gys Tizio ny gys Tifo:
125 shoh foddee cur dooin shen ta aagail ayn;
126 agh crom ort hene as ny jean dty veeal çheu.

133 Tra veih haink Virgilio dy ghoaill greim aym,
134 dooyrt eh rhym: «Tar mygeayrt, dy voddym greim y ghoaill ort»;
135 as ren eh shen dy row eh as mish nyn un.

